1. *Pogledaš* li malo bolje, videćeš da je to slika našeg grada. (If you look a little closer, you will see that it is a picture of our town.)

2. On je *pogledao* u mene sa osmehom. (He looked at me with a smile.)

3. Ona je *pogledala* u nebo. (She looked up at the sky.)

4. *Pogledaš* li bolje, video bi. (If you look closer, you would see it.)

5. On je *pogledao* u knjigu. (He looked into the book.)

6. *Pogledaš* li malo bolje, video bi da se sve promenilo. (If you look a little closer, you would see that everything has changed.)